<%- include("../partials/header") %>

<form class="form" action="/settings/diagnostics/run-test" method="get" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to run a diagnostics test? This will not change anything.')">
  <a class="form__link" href="/settings">Back</a>
  <div class="form__title">Diagnostics</div>
  <p class="form__description">
    Running a diagnostics tests will check the system for discrepancies that can be caused by unexpected errors. What the test confirms:
    <ul class="form__list">
      <li>Meetings, members, tutors, and tutees have unique dates/IDs</li>
      <li>Meetings' and members' attendance records match, with no duplicates</li>
      <li>Members, tutors, and tutees are correctly linked together</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
  <div class="form__item">
    <button class="form__button" type="submit">Run Diagnostics Test</button>
  </div>
</form>

